                            <comment id="12763090" author="ernst.eibensteiner" created="Wed, 7 Oct 2009 15:12:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Link is not valid any more. Please use attached zip to reproduce the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12772355" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 1 Nov 2009 19:01:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue is solved with version 831727. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-549&quot; title=&quot;Lost links when merging with PDFMergerUtility (PDFMergerUtility does not merge Dests)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-549&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-549&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for further details&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12773908" author="ernst.eibensteiner" created="Thu, 5 Nov 2009 12:00:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve downloaded the latest source from &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.eu.apache.org/repos/asf/incubator/pdfbox/trunk/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.eu.apache.org/repos/asf/incubator/pdfbox/trunk/&lt;/a&gt; to test the patch from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-549&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-549&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
But i still get the error above. &quot;The handle is invalid&quot;.&lt;br/&gt;
It seems that the order is also important:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ghostscript1.pdf ComSquare1.pdf ... does not work&lt;br/&gt;
ComSquare1.pdf Ghostscript1.pdf ... works&lt;br/&gt;
Ghostscript2.pdf ComSquare2.pdf ...  does not work&lt;br/&gt;
ComSquare2.pdf Ghostscript2.pdf ... works&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12842628" author="ernst.eibensteiner" created="Mon, 8 Mar 2010 11:26:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;According to the issue &lt;a href=&quot;http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-497&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-497&lt;/a&gt; I tried to close the source files after closing the destination file in PDFMergeUtility.java&lt;br/&gt;
To avoid unclosed file handles I decided to add each source file to a vector and close it afterwards in a loop.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please find attached the patch. I would like you to validate the patch.&lt;br/&gt;
Thx&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12842629" author="ernst.eibensteiner" created="Mon, 8 Mar 2010 11:28:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Please find attached  patch as mentioned above.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12850686" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 28 Mar 2010 15:59:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve applied the patch with version 928439.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thnaks to Ernst for the contribution&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
